OL,3,CScots responding to SNP's positive
OL,4,Cmessage of hope, says Swinney
OL,6,FVoters are responding to the SNP's
OL,7,F"positive message of hope", John
OL,8,FSwinney has said ahead of the final
OL,9,Fweekend of campaigning before
OL,10,FThursday's election.
OL,12,FThe First Minister will take the
OL,13,Fparty's campaign to Glasgow and
OL,14,FEdinburgh on Saturday, as he pledged
OL,15,Fto work "ever harder" to win votes.
OL,17,FWith the cost of living being a key
OL,18,Fissue for voters amid the US-Israeli
OL,19,Foffensive in Iran, the First Minister
OL,20,Fhas committed his party to seek to
OL,21,Fdrive down bills.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@ZO]wD@IOUwD@UO]
