OL,3,CScots responding to SNP's positive
OL,4,Cmessage of hope, says Swinney
OL,6,FThe SNP has pledged in its manifesto
OL,7,Fto cap bus fares at #2 and to
OL,8,Fimplement a price ceiling on essential
OL,9,Ffood items in large supermarkets.
OL,11,FBut the plans to cap food prices have
OL,12,Fbeen criticised by the industry and
OL,13,Fcould face a significant legal
OL,14,Fchallenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
