OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777680175
OL,3,CScots responding to SNP's positive
OL,4,Cmessage of hope, says Swinney
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the final weekend of
OL,7,Fcampaigning, the First Minister said:
OL,8,F"Throughout this campaign, the SNP has
OL,9,Ftaken our positive, ambitious message
OL,10,Fto the people of Scotland about how we
OL,11,Fwill improve the NHS, support people
OL,12,Fwith the cost of living, and deliver
OL,13,Fthe fresh start of independence.
OL,15,F"It is clear that people are
OL,16,Fresponding to that positive message of
OL,17,Fhope ` but between now and polling
OL,18,Fday, the SNP will be working ever
OL,19,Fharder to earn and re-earn people's
OL,20,Ftrust.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777680175
OL,3,CScots responding to SNP's positive
OL,4,Cmessage of hope, says Swinney
OL,6,F"As First Minister, I want to take
OL,7,Faction to support people ` reducing
OL,8,Fthe cost of your daily commute,
OL,9,Fcapping the cost of essential foods in
OL,10,Fsupermarkets, and bringing down
OL,11,Felectricity bills with the fresh start
OL,12,Fof independence.
OL,14,F"The SNP wants to lower your bills,
OL,15,Fand the other parties are trying to
OL,16,Fstop us. They want people to vote for
OL,17,Fan opposition to stop things
OL,18,Fhappening, I am asking people to vote
OL,19,Ffor an SNP government to get things
OL,20,Fdone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777680175
OL,3,CScots responding to SNP's positive
OL,4,Cmessage of hope, says Swinney
OL,6,F"The best way to ensure we can deliver
OL,7,Fis by electing a majority SNP
OL,8,Fgovernment ` one that supports people
OL,9,Fwith the cost of living, locks out
OL,10,FNigel Farage and delivers the fresh
OL,11,Fstart of independence."
OL,13,FBut Scottish Lib Dem deputy leader
OL,14,FWendy Chamberlain said a third decade
OL,15,Fof the SNP in power would "do Scotland
OL,16,Fno good".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@WO]wD@[OUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
