OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777680175
OL,3,CScots responding to SNP's positive
OL,4,Cmessage of hope, says Swinney
OL,6,F"To hear a party that's been in
OL,7,Fgovernment for 19 years promise
OL,8,FScotland a 'fresh start' is downright
OL,9,Fsurreal. I'm not sure who John Swinney
OL,10,Fexpects to believe him," she said.
OL,12,F"If the SNP were serious about
OL,13,Fbringing down the cost of living, they
OL,14,Fmight have a better record to run on.
OL,15,FInstead, they've proposed a baffling
OL,16,Ffood price cap policy that wouldn't be
OL,17,Fin the Scottish Parliament's power to
OL,18,Fdeliver, and which they've had to
OL,19,Frework almost daily since they
OL,20,Fannounced it because it doesn't stand
OL,21,Fup to the barest of scrutiny.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777680175
OL,3,CScots responding to SNP's positive
OL,4,Cmessage of hope, says Swinney
OL,6,F"The SNP's record on the economy is
OL,7,Fone of overpromising, underdelivering,
OL,8,Fand shifting the blame. A third decade
OL,9,Fof that will do Scotland no good."
OL,11,FScottish Tory deputy leader Rachael
OL,12,FHamilton said: "If John Swinney really
OL,13,Fcared about the cost-of-living crisis,
OL,14,Fhe would not have saddled hard-pressed
OL,15,FScots with the highest taxes in the UK.
OL,17,F"Everyone knows that his Soviet-style
OL,18,Ffood price cap is an unworkable
OL,19,Fgimmick designed to create a spat with
OL,20,Fthe UK Government.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]tD@POUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
