CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777680175
OL,3,CScots responding to SNP's positive
OL,4,Cmessage of hope, says Swinney
OL,6,F"Households across Scotland are
OL,7,Fdesperate for some respite from
OL,8,Fconstantly rising bills under the SNP.
OL,9,FThat's why the Scottish Conservatives
OL,10,Fwould cut income tax for all by
OL,11,Freining in out-of-control welfare
OL,12,Fspending."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]
